😍DEEP CONDITION TREATMENT to SMOOTH your hair!!

🤗Every time the weather starts to get colder, I like to give myself a hot oil treatment to prevent my hair from getting dry/brittle/staticy/b during the cold months. This is what I use, and HAVE been using during the season changes since 2012!
.
👌🏾This will DEEP CONDITION
👌🏾HELP it GROW FASTER.
👌🏾SMOOTHEN
👌🏾MOISTURIZE
👌🏾FIGHT DANDRUFF
👌🏾HEAL SCALP
👌🏾And give you HEALTHY HAIR overall!
.
😛I know its annoying to oil your hair because its hard to wash out.. but NOT WITH THIS OIL! Its SO lightweight but hella moisturizing and washes out super easily without weighing your hair down
.
👇🏽ALL YOU NEED:
🍇4 OZ GRAPESEED OIL - ANY OTHER OIL WILL WORK BUTTTT IT WILL BE HEAVIER! If you want something that washes out easily and doesn’t linger in your hair after washing, GET GRAPESEED OIL! 🌸20 DROPS LAVENDER ESSENTIAL OIL (you can skip this, or replace it with rosemary or peppermint.. I just like the scent of lavender and I like it for my scalp)
🌪MIX!
🔥Let the mixture sit in a bowl of HOT WATER until it gets WARM.. NOT BOILING FRY SOME CHICKEN ON URSELF HOT.. just warm.
🙆🏽‍♀️Apply to scalp and all over your hair. SATURATE YOUR HAIR!! YOU WANT TO LOOK LIKE A GREASY MESS! .
🌞I like to add some heat to my oiled hair by putting on a shower cap and then wearing this blow dry hat (idk what its called lol I got it from Sallys beauty supply) attached to my blow drier, set on LOW HEAT for 5-10 mins
.
💦WASH THE OIL OUT WITH SHAMPOO.. no need to condition after .
🐴HAVE THE SILKIEST HAIR OF ALL TIME! I let my hair AIR DRY in loose bantu knots .. I didn’t style my hair with any heat or with any product.. the oil left my hair feeling really soft, silky and smooth!
.
😻GREAT FOR ALL HAIR TYPES AND TEXTURES!
.
💯WHY YOU NEED GRAPESEED OIL:
It works amazing for all skin/hair types and sensitive skin!
Its lightweight and washes out easily
It moisturizes INSTANTLY!
Keeps a healthy scalp and prevents dandruff
Give you healthy hair..and the list goes ON! GET SOME GRAPESEED OIL FAM!
.

😵How I KILL MY ACNE and PREVENT DARK SPOTS (hyperpigmentation) for $3

I filmed this video a while ago but never got around posting it because my self doubt took over me. Its really hard to post “bad skin days” in the perfect world of instagram (especially when you’re an “influencer”) .
😊BUT THEN.. I remembered the reason why I started making DIY videos 9 years ago.. and that’s to help. If this video can help just ONE person.. thats all I could ever ask for.. so here I am, putting it all out there and posting one of the worst skin days I’ve had in a really long time. I broke out like I was 13 all over again.. the breakouts I can get over, but my skin gets hyperpigmentation SO fast.. like THANOS SNAP and I have hyperpigmentation
.
🔥so this is what I do to kill the acne, but mostly, prevent it from leaving a dark spot/scar. Ive been doing this for 5+ years and those of you who’ve been watching me for years have noticed that the darkness around my mouth has gotten significantly lighter and its because of this! .
🤓Before I get into the steps, I just want to make it clear that hyperpigmentation isn’t something that goes away overnight. You need to use this consistently, and if you have old hyperpigmentation, it can take much longer to fade and isn’t guaranteed to go away completely, but it WILL fade.. but with that being said, prevention is key and taking care of it right when it happens helps a LOT!
.
🤩I MAKE MY OWN PEEL/EXFOLIATING PADS using just 1 ingredient! .
🍍U NEED FRESH PINEAPPLE JUICE.. juice it yourself or buy it from a store (no added sugar plz) 🥚Put some cotton rounds in a mason jar + soak with the juice
❄️*KEEP refrigerated*
🍌Use this every other night as a peel (use less if your skin is sensitive) 💦Leave on for 15 mins then rinse with lukewarm water
.
🤷🏽‍♀️WHY THIS WORKS:
PINEAPPLE juice has AHA's which gently exfoliate and get rid of dead skin cells.
enzyme BROMELAIN helps to kill + prevent acne.
high in VITAMIN C..helps fade dark spots, brighten skin and make it even .
Disclaimer: Test patch 1st! .

😍$4 #DIY LEAVE IN MIST TO STOP DANDRUFF, STRENGTHEN + PREVENT HAIR LOSS

🤓Get some fenugreek seeds. Like now. You need them! they’re life changing. I have been using this mist for YEARS now on my hair and its one of my fav, most effective diys of all time. You can do so much with one, $4 bag of fenugreek seeds, to have the best hair, skin and health of all time!
.
👌🏾WHAT YOU NEED:
👍🏾1/2 CUP FENUGREEK SEEDS 💧2 CUPS WATER 💨BOIL 🌬LET COOL COMPLETELY
🍓*U CAN ALSO BLEND THE SEEDS AND USE THEM AS A MASK TO GET RIDICULOUSLY GLOWING SKIN! 3 years ago I posted a tutorial on how to do this..Scroll down in my feed!
☔️STRAIN
💦ADD 30 DROPS OF YOUR FAV ESSENTIAL OIL! I LIKE LAVENDER.. the essential oil is necessary if you don’t like the smell of fenugreek. On its own, it smells like curry. I dont mind it cuz curry is delicious, and I like food.. but if you’re sensitive to smells then add the essential oil to mask the natural scent.
⭐️1 TSP VEGETABLE GLYCERINE
🌪MIX IT UP 🔥POUR INTO A SPRAY BOTTLE
.
🌨SPRAY ONTO DAMP HAIR
💃🏽STYLE IF YOU WANT..or LET IT AIR DRY
STORE IN FRIDGE FOR UP TO 4 weeks
.
🤷🏽‍♀️WHY THIS IS AMAZING:
Fenugreek is one of my fav spice/herbs for your overall hair skin and body
FENUGREEK:
-Kills bacteria on the scalp that causes dandruff and with consistent use GETS RID of dandruff
-its slimy “mucilages” coats the hair shaft and makes it ridiculously shiny
-regulates oil production so no more getting oily hair fast
-prevents hair loss by making hair stronger
VEGETABLE GLYCERIN:
-im using it in this recipe to help create a slight coating on the hair to prevent heat damage
.

😳HAIR HACK: HOW I TRICK PEOPLE INTO THINKING I WASH MY HAIR
.
🥳I posted this on my stories a while ago and a lot of you have been DM’ing me telling me how much you LOVE this HAIR HACK! So..I thought id post it on my feed for those of you who missed my story🙃
.
🤓THIS is how I get away with not washing my hair for 2 weeks (among other hacks which ill share later)…Ive been doing this trick since ive been in high school because aint nobody wanna get up early just to style their hair. You’ll save 3.1459 million hours and look fresh and cute af and not a single soul will know that you didn’t wash your hair.
.
🍌Just section off the TOP of your hair .. no need to worry about the rest because the top covers the rest :) its like our “clean mask” hiding all the greasy roots underneath. If you have OILY SIDES then section your hair in a T… from top of the ear to top of ear and then going back like how I did.
.
💦WASH THAT SECTION ONLY with shampoo.. and then style it to match the rest of your hair. I’m using a diy leave in growth/heat protectant/shine/strength spray which I’ll have up on my feed soon!
.
🙆🏽‍♀️Boom. Look fresh, clean and like you took so long to style your hair but really you just hair hacked it!! Work smarter not harder my friends. .
❄️*i don’t use dry shampoo as often because it makes my scalp feel icky and heavy*
.
👍🏾LIKE this video for more EASY TIME SAVING HACKS LIKE THIS! And dont forget to TAG A LAZY FRIEND WHO HATES WASHING THEIR HAIR!👇🏽👇🏽
.
🤷🏽‍♀️Disclaimer: not washing your hair is not the same as not showering. Please shower. .
